{
  "stem": "21550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I tend to believe that she did it because she-- she thought it's-- it's the right thing to do, not the money.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But another very interesting story is that after the Russians-- the Russian army marched in, as we were-- we were freed in September of 1944.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that-- after the Russians, the Germans left, she said to us, now you're free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want you anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because she got very-- a lot of criticism from her neighbors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she didn't-- she said, you're free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We corresponded with her for a few years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, somehow, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know it's my fault or it's her fault, but we dropped the contact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was a-- used to be a beautiful villa, and the top two floors were demolished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just the basement and the laundry room and the staff rooms, the-- was intact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had one room looking out to a beautiful, beautiful garden, with beautiful fruit trees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why we decided that-- that if we survive, we'd like to live in the country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So when we came to the United States, we bought a chicken farm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I had a hard time, because I didn't know where-- what came first, the chicken or the egg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't know anything about raising chickens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it turned out that some of the neighbors knew about it, but they were good enough not to denounce us, not to threaten us or-- one day, I remember in the summer, I think it was in '44, in the summer.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A-- somebody came in to buy flowers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would cut flowers from her garden, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
